Package de.hochschule.bremen.minerva.commons.exceptions

Exception Summary
AppConfigurationNotFoundException If the application configuration is not available.
AppConfigurationNotReadableException If the application configuration was not readable.
AppConfigurationNotWritableException If the application configuration was not writable.
CountriesNotInRelationException Two given countries are no neighbours.
CountryOwnerException A player does not own a given country.
DataAccessException This exception is a heavy one.
GameAlreadyStartedException Exception that will thrown if someone tried to do something that is not possible while the game is running.
IsOwnCountryException Exception that will thrown if a player tried to attack an own country.
NoPlayerLoggedInException Exception that will thrown if no player is logged but tried to start a new game session.
NoPlayerSlotAvailableException Exception, that will thrown if no player slot is available in a existing game (full).
NotEnoughArmiesException Tried to attack a country with no enough armies.
NotEnoughPlayersLoggedInException Not enough players logged in for starting a new game.
PlayerAlreadyLoggedInException Tried to login a player twice.
PlayerDoesNotExistException Tried to do a operation on an non-existing player.
PlayerExistsException Tried to create a player that already exists.
WorldDoesNotExistException Tried to request an world that does not exist.
WorldExistsException Tried to save an world that already exists.
WorldFileExtensionException Tried to import an world file that does not have the correct file extension.
WorldFileNotFoundException The importable world file was not found.
WorldFileParseException The world from the import file was not parsable, so it is not well-formed.
WorldNotDefinedException Exception that will thrown if someone tried to do something that is not possible if no world was defined (e. g. starting a game).
WorldNotStorable Exception that will be thrown if it is not possible to store an world (e. g. hurt a unique-constraint, etc.).
WrongPasswordException Entered a wrong password while login process.
